column3: Transform yourself with this full body workout using unique exercises and movements. Burn, sculpt and chisel a new you!
Beginning with a cardio warm-up, Jeff will take you through pilates & yoga moves plus free weights for your ultimate body.
A series of mat-based exercises for strength & flexibility.
Build core strength & tone all-over with the use of props.
Flows like ashtanga yoga and threads the core beliefs of pilates, resistance training and yoga together - all to funky music!
A slower paced, less rigorous, softer class for all ages.
Based on the teachings of living Yoga master BKS Iyengar, focusing on strength, flexibility & alignment.\r\n\r\n
Flowing sequences of poses, emphasizes breath awareness.
a high intensity cardio class, incorporating light weights in the 2nd half of class for upper body toning, followed by abs and butt.
Wake your body up with Cait’s morning sculpt.
